# NOTE: pnpm 9 has NO `ignore-workspace` .npmrc key — it is a CLI flag only.
# A plain `pnpm install` here attaches remotion as an importer in the ROOT
# pnpm-lock.yaml (silent workspace pollution). Always install/add standalone:
#   pnpm install --ignore-workspace
#   pnpm add <pkg> --ignore-workspace
# The workspace-hygiene test (scripts/workspace-hygiene.test.ts) fails if the
# root lockfile ever gains a `remotion:` importer.
